      <title>朝鲜在边境部署数百个新型导弹发射器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/north-korea-deploys-hundreds-of-new-missile-launchers-at-border</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜表示，已部署 250 辆新型机动弹道导弹发射器，可对韩国和美国在朝鲜的基地实施核打击，这是朝鲜在领导人金正恩领导下最大规模的火箭实力展示之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/north-korea-deploys-hundreds-of-new-missile-launchers-at-border</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 02:32:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大拒绝马杜罗宣称在委内瑞拉取得胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/canada-minister-rejects-maduro-s-claim-of-victory-in-venezuela</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大谨慎介入委内瑞拉选举争议，拒绝接受尼古拉斯·马杜罗政府公布的官方结果，但没有宣布反对派候选人埃德蒙多·冈萨雷斯为合法获胜者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/canada-minister-rejects-maduro-s-claim-of-victory-in-venezuela</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 01:58:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国爆发骚乱后斯塔默召开紧急会议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/starmer-calls-emergency-meeting-after-riots-flare-across-britain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默召开紧急安全会议，试图平息震惊英国各地社区的反移民抗议活动，这些抗议活动有可能使刚刚成立一个月的政府陷入两极分化的文化争论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/starmer-calls-emergency-meeting-after-riots-flare-across-britain</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马里因支持叛军与乌克兰断绝外交关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/mali-cuts-diplomatic-ties-with-ukraine-for-supporting-rebels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马里军事领导层因乌克兰涉嫌支持马里图阿雷格叛军联盟而断绝了与乌克兰的外交关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/mali-cuts-diplomatic-ties-with-ukraine-for-supporting-rebels</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 22:45:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>凉爽天气和湿度助力加州消防员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-04/cooler-weather-helps-firefighters-corral-a-third-of-massive-california-blaze</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州奇科（美联社）——消防官员周日表示，消防队员正在扑灭加州今年最大的山火，部分原因是天气转凉，他们已经控制住了三分之一的火势，但三位数的气温回升可能导致火势进一步蔓延。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-04/cooler-weather-helps-firefighters-corral-a-third-of-massive-california-blaze</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 21:45:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡马拉·哈里斯即将做出决定，她将与可能的竞选搭档会面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/kamala-harris-to-meet-with-possible-running-mates-as-her-decision-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，副总统卡马拉·哈里斯周日会见了至少三位可能的竞选伙伴：亚利桑那州参议员马克·凯利、宾夕法尼亚州州长乔什·夏皮罗和明尼苏达州州长蒂姆·沃尔兹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/kamala-harris-to-meet-with-possible-running-mates-as-her-decision-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 18:18:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国敦促加沙停火，以色列准备应对伊朗袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/israel-braces-for-attack-from-iran-as-us-urges-gaza-cease-fire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国向加沙地带派遣防御增援部队并敦促达成停火协议之际，以色列做好了应对伊朗和当地民兵可能发动的袭击的准备，以报复真主党和哈马斯官员遭暗杀事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/israel-braces-for-attack-from-iran-as-us-urges-gaza-cease-fire</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 16:38:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>骚乱席卷英国，斯塔默誓言严惩“暴徒”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/police-make-at-least-90-arrests-as-far-right-protests-sweep-uk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·斯塔默表示，那些造成英国城镇混乱和混乱的责任人将因他所说的“极右翼暴徒行为”而受到惩罚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/police-make-at-least-90-arrests-as-far-right-protests-sweep-uk</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 09:36:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>警方警告极右翼煽动街头暴力影响资源</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-04/uk-police-warn-far-right-fueled-street-violence-affects-resources-needed-to-investigate-other-crimes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦（美联社）——英国首相基尔·斯塔默强烈谴责周日发生的针对一家庇护寻求者酒店的袭击，该袭击造成至少 10 名警察受伤，其中一人伤势严重，并称这是“极右翼暴徒行为”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-04/uk-police-warn-far-right-fueled-street-violence-affects-resources-needed-to-investigate-other-crimes</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 09:13:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>疑似胡塞导弹袭击集装箱船 两周内首次遇袭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-04/suspected-missile-attack-by-yemen-s-houthi-rebels-hits-container-ship-in-first-attack-in-2-weeks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迪拜，阿拉伯联合酋长国（美联社）——当局周日称，也门胡塞叛军发动的导弹袭击击中了一艘穿越亚丁湾的悬挂利比里亚国旗的集装箱船，这是自以色列空袭以来该组织首次发动袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-04/suspected-missile-attack-by-yemen-s-houthi-rebels-hits-container-ship-in-first-attack-in-2-weeks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 01:54:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
